    • Constructor Detail

      • CustomLocation

        public CustomLocation(Origin backingLocation)
        This class must be backed by a regular OF location to keep track of versions ordering. This information is not strictly required, but loosing it might lead to ordering errors during synchronization. E.g. an old version stored in a client cache might become the new latest version instead of being discarded during synchronization. When conflicts will be exposed by OF's API, this will turn into false positives.
        Parameters:
        backingLocation - Backing OF location. Must not be registered in any Workspace or Server.
